  "snapshot": "Toronto Centreline V2 resource d562d003-d8eb-4b4b-bbdc-8fe694299a21, modified 2026-07-21; Cultural Hotspot POI resource 4d16d132-fe2d-4f79-8269-9ef942d599a8, modified 2026-02-20; EPSG:2952 CSV exports",
