  "status": "include",
  "transform": "Use the complete current Centreline V2 export, retain rows with two valid intersection endpoints, assign dense IDs to all retained intersections, collapse duplicate undirected endpoint pairs to their minimum positive polyline length, and round that EPSG:2952 metric length to a positive integer number of millimetres. Map every Cultural Hotspot POI point to its nearest retained intersection in EPSG:2952; prefixed Interests and Neighbourhood values are source candidate groups, and the exact nearest-distance distribution is audited. No traffic vertex weight is folded into an edge weight because the present solver model is edge-weighted GST."
